## Features

{% if include_cli %}- **CLI Application**: Command-line interface built with Typer{% endif %}
{% if include_web %}- **Web API**: FastAPI-based web application with automatic API documentation{% endif %}
{% if include_gui %}- **GUI Application**: Desktop interface built with Tkinter{% endif %}
{% if include_tui %}- **TUI Application**: Terminal user interface built with Textual{% endif %}
{% if include_worker %}- **Message Queue Worker**: FastStream-based worker for processing messages from {{worker_broker}}{% endif %}
{% if include_c_extensions %}- **C Extensions**: High-performance Cython extensions for computationally intensive tasks{% endif %}
{% if include_pydantic_settings %}- **Configuration Management**: Type-safe settings using Pydantic{% endif %}
- **Type Safety**: Full type hints with mypy, pyright, and other type checkers
- **Code Quality**: Comprehensive linting and formatting with ruff
- **Testing**: pytest with coverage reporting and parallel execution
- **Documentation**: MkDocs-powered documentation with GitHub Pages deployment
- **CI/CD**: Automated testing, building, and publishing across multiple platforms
- **Modern Python**: uv for dependency management, hatch for building

